Package org.wikidata.wdtk.rdf.extensions

This package contains code for extending the RDF exports with helpful data, such as adding links to other linked data sets for certain statements/claims/snaks etc.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    ValueExportExtension<V extends Value>
    Classes that implement this interface export additional data for snaks with certain values.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ExportExtensions
    Class for managing extensions that add data to the RDF export which is not directly given in the data model.
    FreebaseExportExtension
    Export extension for converting Freebase identifiers into Freebase URIs.
    SimpleIdExportExtension
    Export extension for identifiers that are formed by simply putting a URI prefix and postfix around the string value stored in Wikibase.
    StringIdExportExtension
    Simple helper class for implementing value export extensions for the common case that a single Wikibase property of type string is to be translated to a single link to an external URI.
